main event: On April 20, 1952, an individual reported seeing unidentified objects in the sky while taking photographs at Griffith Park Planetarium in Los Angeles, California.
interesting points: The photographs taken were believed to show unusual scenes, which might have imperfections due to the developing process,The sighting occurred about an hour after sunset,Mr. ********* submitted the photographs due to recent media interest in flying saucers,He was accompanied by other individuals who were more focused on the scenery than the sky at the time,The photos were taken on a Kodak camera 15 to 20 seconds apart.
witness description: Mr. ********* and his wife, along with another couple visiting from Wichita, Kansas
